     Looking at the ghost charges problem: if a charge succeeds but the inventory decrement fails, the customer gets charged without receiving the item. The original code has this exact flawтАФwhen payment processing takes longer than inventory decrement, a successful charge followed by a failed decrement means no item is delivered but the customer is still billed.
     
